The paper deals with neural networks and their ability to learn semantic representations by exploiting syntactic information. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV). Among these, cs.CL is the most likely category as the paper specifically mentions the success of tree-structured neural networks in learning semantic representations.
